	* scripts/Windows/Installer/BuildInstaller.bat,
	  scripts/Windows/Installer/NUT-Installer.xml: Change from
	  libgnurx-0.dll to msys-regex-1.dll for the sake of coherency  (use
	  only msys DLLs)
