	* drivers/usbhid-ups.c: reinstate handling for STATUS(ONLINE) in
	  usbhid-ups  The recent onlinedischarge changes removed support for
	  some STATUS(ONLINE) cases, affecting at least CP1300EPFCLCD - this
	  brings them back.

