	  compiler warnings with "ifndef HAVE___ATTRIBUTE__NORETURN" to avoid
	  opposite warnings now
	* server/upsd.c: wrap unreachable exit() added due to earlier
	  compiler warnings with "ifndef HAVE___ATTRIBUTE__NORETURN" to avoid
	  opposite warnings now
