2011-03-18  Arjen de Korte <adkorte-guest@alioth.debian.org>

	* include/Makefile.am: The include/nut_stdint.h file is no longer a
	  generated one (part two)
	* include/Makefile.am: The include/nut_stdint.h file is no longer a
	  generated one
